    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hotloop is a fast-paced twin-stick space shooter focused on Gravity and Orbiting. You have to curb the force of gravity and learn how to use it to your advantage in order to repel numerous enemies. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >WHAT THIS GAME OFFERS</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Real physics! Say no to jelly space! Absolute inertia! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Dynamic gameplay </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Various enemies with different abilities </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Real orbital maneurs </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Dozens of weapons and modules you can install on your spacecraft </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2253660/extras/9de6cb89242311a30b1f8fea5e7c62d9.poster.avif?t=1762089767\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2253660/extras/9de6cb89242311a30b1f8fea5e7c62d9.webm?t=1762089767\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2253660/extras/9de6cb89242311a30b1f8fea5e7c62d9.mp4?t=1762089767\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >USE ENVIRONMENT TO DEFEAT ENEMIES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Smash them into the asteroid field </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make them burn near the sun </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make them fall into hugs of a black hole </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2253660/extras/16e3d8810460194c6e1a0adcfb3e68e7.poster.avif?t=1762089767\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2253660/extras/16e3d8810460194c6e1a0adcfb3e68e7.webm?t=1762089767\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2253660/extras/16e3d8810460194c6e1a0adcfb3e68e7.mp4?t=1762089767\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >USE ORBITS TO YOUR ADVANTAGE</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Save some spare fuel </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make enemies struggle trying to shoot you </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Or just take a cup of tea, you are on an orbit anyway</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2253660/extras/840b57c0ecae42fca573422d0660e0ad.poster.avif?t=1762089767\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2253660/extras/840b57c0ecae42fca573422d0660e0ad.webm?t=1762089767\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2253660/extras/840b57c0ecae42fca573422d0660e0ad.mp4?t=1762089767\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >USE DIFFERENT SYSTEMS TO SUPPRESS YOUR ENEMIES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > EMP </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gravity field generators </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Deadly blast waves generator</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Only you chose how to fight in this game.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2253660/extras/ddddfbdc7f377485620ed8c530e1fdec.poster.avif?t=1762089767\" width=600 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2253660/extras/ddddfbdc7f377485620ed8c530e1fdec.webm?t=1762089767\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2253660/extras/ddddfbdc7f377485620ed8c530e1fdec.mp4?t=1762089767\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >EXPERIMENT WITH YOUR WEAPONRY </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There is plenty of guns </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Lasers </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Plasma guns </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rocket launchers </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > SHOTGUNS</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2253660/extras/d1f9702ee5cdf3cc873b9549ea5350f1.poster.avif?t=1762089767\" width=600 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2253660/extras/d1f9702ee5cdf3cc873b9549ea5350f1.webm?t=1762089767\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2253660/extras/d1f9702ee5cdf3cc873b9549ea5350f1.mp4?t=1762089767\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >TRY YOUR BEST ON DIFFERENT MAPS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get on top of the leaderboard on ehach of the locations.</p>",
